Learn all the benefits you can get from this amazing program.  How to register for Amazon Video Direct and make your account ready immediately.  Learn what’s the best video format to be uploaded to Amazon Video Direct.  The easy simple way to make sure your videos look perfect on any screen sizes.  Prepare your video before you upload it. Make sure you include closed caption and create the most attracting video cover.  How to upload video to your Amazon Video Direct account without any issues. How to choose the right pricing and monetization options for all of your videos.  Learn how to analyze your video performance metrics to optimize the way you offer your next videos.
